{"tid":916464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「解釋你聽」煩請泛民同李卓人支持者入一入黎","createTime":"2018-11-25T17:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T05:33:52.000Z","uid":7971,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cfded5065c2c1537f9bdfbff1cd39fc125047a3","tid":916464,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"<del>廢時屌關鍵最後一席 去咗日本旅行/無人開會<br />\n都廢時同你互屌 有險可守同 DQ咗 仲話香港係自由選舉</del><br />\n<br />\n有咩理由 <br />\n游b個位 就話屬於人民 所以有初選<br />\n但小麗老母個位 就係屬於老母 初選都無啊？<br />\n<br />\n你班飯民 依家空降一個新西人入九西 <br />\n之後屌個九西做咗30年嘅人係鎅票？<br />\n<br />\n口講爭取民主 但連初選都無 <br />\n仲要欽點一個人 話係佢就係佢 咁叫咩民主啊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答我啊！ 民主派支持者！"},{"pid":"6d74826498874b31ec511417416445344f711129","tid":916464,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bd376a7868128fe268fa101a582af6ed3f2460","tid":916464,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"本土派既野即係我既野<br />\n而我既野即係我既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a45ef2f925ed56ab10454daa37334a904aae8db","tid":916464,"uid":31151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"話係屬於老母都算 點解plan b冇初選?"},{"pid":"538ea55245445df49ca096be3617fcbaff64d2d9","tid":916464,"uid":7971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f3bd376a7868128fe268fa101a582af6ed3f2460","tid":916464,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"本土派既野即係我既野<br />\n而我既野即係我既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"真係好撚on9 <br />\n係未臭都要含 仲要含足30年含到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.